file.name: fdi-rest.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.2"
info:
  title: "FDI API 接口"
  description: "贸金区块链平台与贸易联动对接项目 FDI API 接口"
  version: "0.5"

servers:
  - url: http://localhost:3000/api/v1/

paths:
  /events:
    get:
      tags:
        - 搜寻事件
      summary: "搜寻事件"
      operationId: events
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/events'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/entities'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/submitters'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/submittedAfter'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/submittedBefore'
      responses:
        200:
          description: 成功响应
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                title: 事件序列
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Event'
        401:
          description: 未获受权
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Unauthorized'
        404:
          description: 未能找到
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/NotFound'

  /pos:
    get:
      tags: 
        - 搜寻订单
      summary: "搜寻订单"
      operationId: pos
      parameters: 
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/descriptions'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/submitters'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/createdAfter'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/createdBefore'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/updatedAfter'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/updatedBefore'
      responses:
        200:
          description: 成功响应
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                title: 订单序列
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/PO'
        401:
          description: 未获受权
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Unauthorized'
        404:
          description: 未能找到
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/NotFound'

  /invoices:
    get:
      tags:
        - 搜寻发票
      summary: "搜寻发票"
      operationId: invoices
      parameters: 
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/descriptions'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/submitters'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/createdAfter'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/createdBefore'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/updatedAfter'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/updatedBefore'
      responses:
        200:
          description: 成功响应
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                title: 发票序列
                type: array
                items:
                  $ref: '#/components/schemas/Invoice'
        401:
          description: 未获受权
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Unauthorized'
        404:
          description: 未能找到
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/NotFound'

components:
  parameters:
    events:
      name: events
      in: query
      description: "事件种类"
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          type: string
      required: false
      explode: true

    entities:
      name: entities
      in: query
      description: "单元种类"
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          type: string
          enum: [PO, Invoice]
      required: false
      explode: true

    submittedAfter:
      name: submittedAfter
      in: query
      description: "提交时间 - 开始 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)"
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
      required: false

    submittedBefore:
      name: submittedBefore
      in: query
      description: "提交时间 - 结束 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)"
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
      required: false

    descriptions:
      name: descriptions
      in: query
      description: "单元描述"
      schema:
        type: string
      required: false

    submitters:
      name: submitters
      in: query
      description: "提交者号码"
      schema:
        type: array
        items:
          type: string
      required: false
      explode: true

    createdAfter:
      name: createdAfter
      in: query
      description: "创建时间 - 开始 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)"
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
      required: false

    createdBefore:
      name: createdBefore
      in: query
      description: "创建时间 - 结束 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)"
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
      required: false

    updatedAfter:
      name: updatedAfter
      in: query
      description: "最后更新时间 - 开始 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)"
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
      required: false

    updatedBefore:
      name: updatedBefore
      in: query
      description: "最后更新时间 - 结束 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)"
      schema:
        type: integer
        format: int64
      required: false

  schemas:
    Event:
      title: 事件
      type: object
      required:
        - commitId
        - entityType
        - eventSubmitter
        - eventTypes
        - submittedDate
      properties:
        commitId:
          type: string
          description: 事件内码
        entityType:
          type: string
          description: 单元种类
          enum: [PO, Invoice]
        eventSubmitter:
          type: string
          description: 提交者号码
          example: "eTradeConnect"
        eventTypes:
          type: array
          description: 事件种类
          items:
            type: string
        submittedDate:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          description: 事件提交时间 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)

    PO:
      title: 订单
      type: object
      required:
        - poNumber
        - poDescription
        - poSubmitter
        - poCreateDate
        - poUpdateDate
      properties:
        poNumber:
          type: string
          description: 订单号码
        poDescription:
          type: string
          description: 订单描述
        poSubmitter:
          type: string
          description: 订单提交者
          example: "eTradeConnect"
        poCreateDate:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          description: 订单创建时间 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)
        poUpdateDate:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          description: 订单最后更新时间 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)

    Invoice:
      title: 发票
      type: object
      required:
        - invoiceNumber
        - invoiceDescription
        - invoiceSubmitter
        - invoiceCreateDate
        - invoiceUpdateDate
      properties:
        invoiceNumber:
          type: string
          description: 发票号码
        invoiceDescription:
          type: string
          description: 发票描述
        invoiceSubmitter:
          type: string
          description: 发票提交者
          example: "eTradeConnect"
        invoiceCreateDate:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          description: 发票创建时间 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)
        invoiceUpdateDate:
          type: integer
          format: int64
          description: 发票最后更新时间 (百份秒, Unix epoch 时间)

    Unauthorized:
      type: string
      description: 未获受权 (401)
      example: 访问未获受权

    NotFound:
      type: string
      description: 未能找到 (404)
      example: 未能找到资源

Error: notImplemented: path "/events": get: responses: 401: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
